@startuml
title Request Quotation Sequence Diagram

actor Customer
participant "WhatsApp Bot\n(src/bot.js)" as Bot
participant "Catalog Helpers\n(src/botHelpers.js)" as Catalog
participant "Pricing Service\n(src/pricing.js)" as Pricing
participant "Order Utils\n(src/orderUtils.js)" as Utils
participant "Invoice Service\n(src/invoice.js)" as Invoice

Customer -> Bot : Select Goods/Services and product
Bot -> Catalog : buildCatalog(config)
Catalog --> Bot : available product options
Customer -> Bot : Enter dimensions or quantity
Bot -> Pricing : calculatePrice(productKey, width, height, quantity)
Pricing --> Bot : quote result
Bot -> Utils : calculateCartTotals(cart)
Utils --> Bot : updated totals
Bot --> Customer : Show estimate summary
Customer -> Bot : Finish and get PDF
Bot -> Utils : buildOrderFromCart(...)
Utils --> Bot : estimate order model
Bot -> Invoice : generateInvoicePDF(order, fileName, "ESTIMATE")
Invoice --> Bot : PDF path
Bot --> Customer : Send estimate PDF

@enduml
